End of day update (from https://talk.oceanheart.online/#narrow/stream/4-accountability/topic/Q1.3AWeek-3/near/1126):

  • Added weekly accountability report generation to Gates bot
  • built out the core graph engine for Ben
  • got a bit distracted writing utility scripts for Ben; built a web crawler that ingests code docs online and creates markdown files with code examples to make more specific LLM code generation prompts. Mission successful.

Reflections on yesterday:

  • In brief, I had successfully managed to tunnel my way into an approach that proved to be far deeper than I ever imagined.
  • A complete architectural overhaul; only now I have but hours to implement it, rather than days.
  • It might not even be possible. But I'm going in anyway.
